---
title: Glazed Pork Tenderloin with Basmati Rice and Veggie Jumble
description: This Asian-inspired meal packs in all the flavor of your restaurant favorites. The only difference? It’s way healthier. Lean pork tenderloins are roasted with soy sauce, honey, and a bit of Dijon mustard. Then, they’re plated on top of a colorful bed of blistered snow peas, bell peppers, carrots, scallions, and hearty rice.
